                        <a href="@Az900Url" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-reset link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Azure Fundamentals (AZ-900)</a> •
                        <a href="@Ai900Url" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-reset link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Azure AI Fundamentals (AI-900)</a> •
                        <a href="@Dp900Url" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-reset link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Azure Data Fundamentals (DP-900)</a> •
